com.indragie.cmput301as1

Interface TypedObserver<T>

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ElasticSearchQueue, ExpenseClaimDetailActivity, ExpenseClaimDetailController, ExpenseClaimListController, ManageTagsActivity, Session, TagAddToClaimActivity, TagEditToClaimActivity

    public interface TypedObserver<T>
    Interface implemented by classes when they want to be informed of changes in observable objects. This class is the same as Observer, except that the argument passed into update(TypedObservable, T) is typed.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      void update(TypedObservable<T> o, T arg)
      Informs the observer that the observable has been updated.

      • update

        void update(TypedObservable<T> o,
            T arg)
        Informs the observer that the observable has been updated.
        Parameters:
        o - The observable that was updated.
        arg - An optional argument containing data that can be used by the observer to update itself (e.g. updating UI)
